Chapter0101

연습문제

1-6

1. \(f(x)=1+x^2\)
curve(1+x^2, -5, 5)

2. \(f(x)=1-\sqrt(x)\)
curve(1-sqrt(x), 0, 100)

3. \(f(x)=\frac{1}{\sqrt(x)}\)
curve(1/sqrt(x), 0, 100)

4. \(f(x)=\frac{1}{1+\sqrt{x}}\)
curve(1/(1+sqrt(x)), 0, 100)

5. \(f(x)=\sqrt{4-x^2}\)
curve(sqrt(4-x^2), -2.0, 2.0)

6. \(f(x)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{9-x^2}}\)
curve(1/sqrt(9-x^2), -3.0, 3.0)

7. \(y=\sqrt{\frac{1}{x}-1}\)
curve(sqrt(1/x-1), 0, 1)

8. \(y=\sqrt{2-\sqrt{x}}\)
curve(sqrt(2-sqrt(x)), 0, 4)

2-5. \(f(x)=\frac{x}{|\,x\,|}\)
curve(x/abs(x), -5.0, 5.0)
